              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>The patient shows mildly elevated HbA1c, indicating suboptimal long-term glycemic control (prediabetes/early diabetes). All other parameters, including renal function and electrolytes, are within normal limits except for a slightly low total CO₂, which may suggest mild metabolic acidosis or compensation. No acute abnormalities detected; recommend monitoring glycemic control and clinical correlation for acid-base status.</td></tr></table></div>"
